rComments: I don't like him. He doesn't explain what we're doing before we do it, and his explanations are hard to understand. He makes a fair amount of mistakes, and rushes through the topics without going over them properly. He's a chill person but I absolutely hate his lectures. His notes don't make sense unless you go to class, and even so they're bad.
Very good prof. Lectures are very fast, and you better take notes of the examples. He answers questions at the end. Very good explaining stuff during office hours.
Best calc prof I ever had. The boss of the math world
very on time if he shows up
